org.javafp.parsecj

Interface ConsumedT<S,A>

  • Type Parameters:
    S - Input stream symbol type.
    A - Parse result type

    public interface ConsumedT<S,A>
    ConsumedT is a discriminated union between a Consumed type and an Empty type. Wraps a parse result (Reply) and indicates whether the parser consumed input in the process of computing the parse result.
